values:
I am so happy and so proud. I bawled my eyes out last night as CNN announced that Obama had won. I was so nervous and scared but now I am nothing but hopeful and thrilled! Many tears of happiness, let me tell you :)

And I never thought I'd see the day, but Indiana of all places is going to Obama! My actual vote MEANT SOMETHING!

Good plan - working out with Wii Fit
Bad plan - getting a mocha frappuccino
Worse plan - drinking mocha frappuccino right before exercising on Wii Fit
Wow, my journal is a pretty boring place (not like it's that interesting overall, but still) if you're not on my friends list. Comment if you want added.

It feels so strange not not have to think about leveling this character anymore. I did more questing that I've ever done in the game before, and I had a lot of fun, I have to say. I don't know where I would be without coords mods though, oh man! I'm now exceptionally poor from buying my lovely Snowy Gryphon and riding skill, and within the first 5 minutes, I had already fallen to my death from thinking I was on the edge of a ledge and dismounting. Spirit rez ftl :( Time to get the shadow priest past level 61 finally now, hehe :)

21 March 03 -

MEREDITH -

I think it's way adorable that my cat snores ever so quietly :) She's sacked out on top of my dresser, curled up in a towel :)
I thought that I'd read that paid users can cash in their unused codes for more paid time. How do I go about doing this?
My cat is so smart that she just singed off some of her fur whilst sitting next to a candle

Imagine there's no heaven, It's easy if you try, No hell below us, Above us only sky, Imagine all the people living for today... Imagine there's no countries, It isnt hard to do, Nothing to kill or die for, No religion too, Imagine all the people living life in peace... Imagine no possesions, I wonder if you can, No need for greed or hunger, A brotherhood of man, Imagine all the people Sharing all the world... You may say Im a dreamer, but Im not the only one, I hope some day you'll join us, And the world will live as one.
I've decided that I'm going to decorate my new room in an ocean type theme. I'm so very excited!
Ketchup is sacred. Do not fuck with my ketchup
You know, Sunny Delight is really good stuff. I wish that I could have finished my bottle of it before it disappeared out of the fridge

I get to take Lennon to work with me today and let her run around behind the desk! I'm leaving for my mom's house straight from work, so my boss said that I can bring Lennon in all day, yay!

Have a good Thanksgiving everyone :)

I can see little flakes of snow falling when I look out my window. I refuse to believe! NO SNOW! Snow is bad!

I hope I don't look at the ground and see that the snow is sticking...

Mwa ha ha! Tonight on Ebay I won both "Legacy of the Wizard" (for 1 cent! plus S/H of course) and "Time Lord" (for 99 cents! plus S/H again) which are two NES games that I used to play all the time. Whoo!!!

I won't become an Ebay addict, I won't become an Ebay Addict, I won't become an Ebay aaddict...
I have turned to the dark side. I made an ebay account to buy old video games with...
HOLY FUCK GUYS! I WROTE 11940 WORDS TONIGHT IN FIVE HOURS!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!

Wow, you know, I don't know if there is anything as fun as walking into the bathroom, seeing your cat peeing on the floor, then having to literally give her a bath in the bathtub, and then go to change her litterbox to find out that there's no litter, so then you have to run to the store at midnight on a wednesday night to buy cat litter. 

So much fun, let me tell you...
I've written almost 6000 words today, holy crap. I am 10.84 days ahead of schedule, whoo! I really need a shower now. My serial killer just poisoned her first tube of tooth paste

Oh my goodness, I'm a writing fool! I've already got 5001 words down on my story! I've got random character tangents comeing out of nowhere and taking up like 1500 words at a time and stuff. 

I have apparently become a much faster typist also because I've done 5001 words in only 3 hours total!
My DSL is out for who knows how long. This sucks hardcore. I hope it'll eventually get fixed or else I'll go frickin INSANE
Look! I'm in the paper for NaNoWriMo!

My LiveJournal Trick-or-Treat Haul
decemberjuliet goes trick-or-treating, dressed up as 50's girl.
nothardcore gives you 10 dark blue raspberry-flavoured wafers.
nightsong gives you 12 yellow coconut-flavoured pieces of chewing gum.
necessarystory tricks you! You get a piece of string.
randomfurie tricks you! You get a used tissue.
lilacgirl gives you 1 light blue lime-flavoured gummies.
randomcyn gives you 4 light orange orange-flavoured gummy fruits.
atomicnumber51 gives you 5 light yellow peach-flavoured nuggets.
therewaslight gives you 3 light blue watermelon-flavoured gummy worms.
pinkstargoddess gives you 12 red orange-flavoured pieces of chewing gum.
kashi gives you 8 teal banana-flavoured pieces of bubblegum.
decemberjuliet ends up with 55 pieces of candy, a piece of string, and a used tissue.

Hey everyone, the Bloomington NaNoWriMo group will be having its kick off party this Tuesday at 8:30pm at La Torre. All of the details can be found here. If you are Planning on coming, please RSVP in that thread by Tuesday morning so that I can make reservations for us. Thanks!

Today I did something that I hadn't done since 3 Sept 1996, I PARALLEL PARKED! And even better, I didn't hit the cars or the curb, and it only took me ONE TRY!

I realise this sounds silly to you guys, but it's a big deal to me :)
My LJ friends list is just overpowering so I'm going to whittle it down some. Please don't take offense, I just can't keep up with everyone anymore

I really want to be in another musical.

Ever since I was a little kid, I was always profoundly interested in secret codes and the like, and reading "The Da Vinci Code" has made me even more interested in cryptology and symbology. Perhaps I'll go to the library very soon...

I started reading The Da Vinci Code by Dan Brown last night and oh holy crap this is a wonderful book. I'm already on page 261. It's be far the most interesting and compelling books I've ever read, if not the most interesting and compelling. Go read it NOW Edit - 12:10am - I just finished the book. Wow.....
